lead_paragraph: Looking to fill a rare gap on its medal shelf, Team USA is sending the strongest fencing squad in memory to Rio, helped along by a generation of Olympic elders that has expanded the sport's frontiers.

headline.print_headline: 'Best U.S. Team' Set for High Profile in Brazil
